<p style="color:gray">CUSTOMS CALCULATION</p>
<hr>
The item purchased in our online store can be returned or exchanged within 14 calendar days from the date it is received.
The product can be returned and exchanged for a similar product if the product is defective by the manufacturer or if the product is not suitable (in size, color, etc.).
Return of goods is possible under the following conditions:
if from the moment of purchase of the goods passed no more than 14 days (excluding the day of purchase);
the goods are in good condition, the goods have not been used, preserved the consumer goods and the appearance;
if there is a document confirming the purchase of the specified product.
If, at the time of exchange, a similar product is not available, you can:
to purchase any other product with a corresponding transfer of value;
to exchange goods for the same at the first time it is received on sale;
get back the amount for the purchased product.
